<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1379270-why-does-the-play-have-this-name">Why does the play have this name?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1379270'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F847168.A_View_from_the_Bridge">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1379270-why-does-the-play-have-this-name">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1379270-why-does-the-play-have-this-name">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
