<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1313177-how-does-the-playwright-handle-the-italian">How does the playwright handle the Italian accents of the immigrants?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1313177'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F847168.A_View_from_the_Bridge">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1313177-how-does-the-playwright-handle-the-italian">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1313177-how-does-the-playwright-handle-the-italian">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/2794271-stephen-sanders"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1396800915i/2794271._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/2794271-stephen-sanders">Stephen Sanders</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">He doesn’t. In the script, the Italian immigrants appear to speak in standard, though relatively simple, English, while the Italian-American Brooklyni<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">He doesn’t. In the script, the Italian immigrants appear to speak in standard, though relatively simple, English, while the Italian-American Brooklynites speak in realistic dialect for the locale and period. In a staged production the director would decide how to portray the immigrant characters’ accents. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
