<span id="freeTextContainer3124680229764700160">A terrifying and tragic play about family dynamics, immigration, law, and the denial of your own sins. I read and saw the play in 2010 when I was actually working on immigration law so I could relate to the aspect of how harsh the law is on both documented and undocumented immigrants.<br/><br/><a href='https://www.flickr.com/photos/eralon/4318848375/' title='Broadway: View from the Bridge 2010' rel='nofollow noopener'>
