        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4502623463" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer587829724865583350">Arthur Miller is undefeated. His plays have so much depth, heart, complexity and timeless humanity. This has been on my list for quite some time. Was a quick read and quite the page turner. It&apos;s an exploration in masculinity, race relations, immigration, and sexuality. Lots to unpack there. </span>
  <span id="freeText587829724865583350" style="display:none">Arthur Miller is undefeated. His plays have so much depth, heart, complexity and timeless humanity. This has been on my list for quite some time. Was a quick read and quite the page turner. It's an exploration in masculinity, race relations, immigration, and sexuality. Lots to unpack there. </span>
